Discord Developer Terms & API Policies

Any violation of Discord policies may result in immediate revocation of access to the Bot.

3. Data Usage & Privacy

The Bot collects only the minimum data necessary to operate (e.g., user IDs, server IDs, command metadata).

The Bot does not sell, share, or misuse user data.

Data may be stored temporarily for functionality, moderation, analytics, or debugging.

Discord may collect and process data independently of the Bot.

